div.p:
If he be in the third eſtate of body, which is a mean betwixt the other extreams, then a moneth or ſix weeks, or a fortnight or leſs, may be time ſufficient to diet him for his Match▪ Now as this eſtate participates with both the former, ſo it wou'd borrow from them a ſhare in all their orderings, that is, to be neither too early, nor too late in airings; 
                     •
                  aborious, but not painfull in heatings, nouriſhing in ſcouring, and conſtant in a moderate way of feeding.
